videos.description: Javonte Smart brings the ball up and throws a slick behind-the-back bounce pass to Skylar Mays, who sinks a deep 3-pointer to give LSU a 27-20 lead over Bowling Green.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (LSU's Smart throws slick behind-the-back pass to Mays for 3) 2019/11/08 ESHEET

videos.headline: LSU's Smart throws slick behind-the-back pass to Mays for 3

videos.description: Javonte Smart runs the break and pushes the ball up to Trendon Watford who takes flight to deliver a devastating jam at the rim.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Watford throws down rim-rattling fast-break jam) 2019/11/08 ESHEET
